{"tid":2346708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"考評局稱管理層無向前經理楊穎宇施壓","createTime":"2020-12-30T12:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T12:39:00.000Z","uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"87fc11ee754c8d85124dfe860cf8193af03033d2","tid":2346708,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】考評局回應一名前僱員指控，稱從無對他施壓。<br />\n<br />\n考評局歷史科評核發展部前經理楊穎宇，近日接受多間媒體訪問，透露在取消歷史科試題後受到壓力而辭職。<br />\n<br />\n考評局發聲明指，委員會及管理層從無向他施壓，亦無指示任何人要求他辭職，又指歷年來文憑試的審題委員會人選皆由考評局全權負責和審批。聲明提到，如有任何人涉嫌洩露保密資料，或發表不符事實的報道和言論，定必嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418491&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSDnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=2ebd025b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418491&h=4e983279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418491</a>"},{"pid":"102489494ae1ee69b6a151408c351e63630fbf80","tid":2346708,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"信你"},{"pid":"bb18534a8f596706513a2b08e6be9f86e5e2dcf4","tid":2346708,"uid":343544,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:32:00.000Z","msg":"聲稱"},{"pid":"7f600bfb02fa5c6f0a5cf522895a0562b07693af","tid":2346708,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"話冇即係有"},{"pid":"504bee19fd4b7e048a010e0b3be581b827c5bae6","tid":2346708,"uid":355064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"單機啦"},{"pid":"fcb07f062f4e5b9bd75fafbb2295b1b03d5b7018","tid":2346708,"uid":123696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"考評局嘅委員會及管理層<br />\n同教育局嘅委員會及管理層<br />\n係兩樣唔同嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif